            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-8">
                This is a portfolio project for demonstration purposes only. 
                <br><br>
                <strong>No real products are sold here.</strong> <br>
                Please do not use real payment information.
            </p>
            <button onclick="dismissDemo()" class="w-full bg-primary text-primary-foreground py-4 rounded-full font-bold hover:shadow-lg hover:opacity-90 active:scale-95 transition-all duration-300">
                I Understand
            </button>
